---
import FeeSystem from "../common/FeeSystem.astro";
---

<section id="price" class="py-20 bg-[#F7F3EE]">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif mb-4">料金・システム</h2>
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-[#A88B58] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.2em] font-serif uppercase"
            >
                <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
                Fees & System
                <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <FeeSystem />

        <div class="mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-center mb-8 text-[#6B5F54]">
                <span class="border-b-2 border-[#A88B58]/30 pb-2"
                    >レッスン回数について</span
                >
            </h3>
            <p class="text-center mb-10 text-sm md:text-base leading-loose">
                月1回〜4回から、<span class="inline-block"
                    >生徒さまのペースに合わせて</span
                ><span class="inline-block">お選びいただけます。</span>
            </p>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 md:gap-6"
            >
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#F1EBE4] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-row items-stretch md:flex-col md:items-center md:justify-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 md:w-auto flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-center text-center border-r border-[#E8E2D9] pr-4 md:border-r-0 md:pr-0 md:mb-4"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="block text-[#A88B58] font-serif font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-widest"
                            >月1回</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center text-left pl-4 md:pl-0 md:text-center"
                    >
                        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#6B5F54]">
                            <span class="inline-block">まずはゆっくり</span><br
                            />
                            <span class="inline-block">始めたい方へ</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#F1EBE4] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-row items-stretch md:flex-col md:items-center md:justify-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 md:w-auto flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-center text-center border-r border-[#E8E2D9] pr-4 md:border-r-0 md:pr-0 md:mb-4"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="block text-[#A88B58] font-serif font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-widest"
                            >月2回</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center text-left pl-4 md:pl-0 md:text-center"
                    >
                        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#6B5F54]">
                            <span class="inline-block">忙しい中でも</span><br />
                            <span class="inline-block"
                                >無理なく続けたい方へ</span
                            >
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#F1EBE4] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-row items-stretch md:flex-col md:items-center md:justify-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 md:w-auto flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-center text-center border-r border-[#E8E2D9] pr-4 md:border-r-0 md:pr-0 md:mb-4"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="block text-[#A88B58] font-serif font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-widest"
                            >月3回</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center text-left pl-4 md:pl-0 md:text-center"
                    >
                        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#6B5F54]">
                            <span class="inline-block">安定したペースで</span
                            ><br />
                            <span class="inline-block">力をつけたい方へ</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#F1EBE4] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-row items-stretch md:flex-col md:items-center md:justify-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 md:w-auto flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-center text-center border-r border-[#E8E2D9] pr-4 md:border-r-0 md:pr-0 md:mb-4"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="block text-[#A88B58] font-serif font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-widest"
                            >月4回</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center text-left pl-4 md:pl-0 md:text-center"
                    >
                        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#6B5F54]">
                            <span class="inline-block">目標に向けて</span><br />
                            <span class="inline-block"
                                >しっかり取り組みたい方へ</span
                            >
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-[#E8E2D9] shadow-sm"
            >
                <h3
                    class="font-serif font-bold text-[#A88B58] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl"
                >
                    レッスン会場について
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-[#6B5F54]">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[#A88B58] mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
                        <span>ご自宅への出張レッスンを行っております。</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[#A88B58] mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
                        <span
                            >会場をレンタルしてのレッスンも可能です。<br />
                            <span class="text-sm text-[#6B5F54] mt-1 block"
                                >※練習室レンタルの場合、別途会場費がかかります。</span
                            ></span
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[#A88B58] mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
                        <span
                            >場所の詳細は、生徒さまのご希望や状況に合わせて検討いたします。</span
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-[#E8E2D9]">
                    <p
                        class="text-sm md:text-base text-left md:text-center text-[#6B5F54] md:text-[#544A40]"
                    >
                        分からないことや聞いておきたいことがございましたら、<span
                            class="md:inline-block"
                            >遠慮なくご連絡ください。</span
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
